<li><a href="https://plato.stanford.edu/entries/turing-machine/">Turing Machines</a> by Liesbeth De Mol.</li>
<li><a href="https://plato.stanford.edu/entries/logic-dependence/">Dependence Logic</a> by Pietro Galliani.</li>
<li><a href="https://plato.stanford.edu/entries/voluntarism-theological/">Theological Voluntarism</a> by Mark Murphy.</li>
<li><a href="https://plato.stanford.edu/entries/lewis-ci/">Clarence Irving Lewis</a> by Bruce Hunter.</li>
<li><a href="https://plato.stanford.edu/entries/square/">The Traditional Square of Opposition</a> by Terence Parsons and Graziana Ciola.</li>
